title: State Secretary Andrejs Pildegoviﾄ行 to take part in the annual Baltic and Nordic State Secretaries ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Latvia ) On 19-20 October, the State Secretary of the Latvian Foreign Ministry , Andrejs Pildegoviﾄ行, will take part in the annual meeting of State Secretaries of the Foreign Ministries
